parameters.name: DtsJobId
parameters.description: The ID of the ETL task. You can call the [DescribeDtsJobs](~~209702~~) operation to query the task ID.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the region in which the Data Transmission Service (DTS) instance resides. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the available Alibaba Cloud regions.
